(Lu Changhe, September 20th, 1916)

13
00:01:58,400 --> 00:01:59,040
(Why?)

14
00:01:59,719 --> 00:02:00,560
(Why?)

15
00:02:01,079 --> 00:02:03,079
(Why we've made so many efforts,)

16
00:02:03,719 --> 00:02:05,439
(yet still end up like this?)

17
00:02:06,159 --> 00:02:08,719
(The world is not fair.)

18
00:02:09,319 --> 00:02:10,560
You look so pretty today.

19
00:02:13,439 --> 00:02:14,199
Miss Mu.

20
00:02:14,479 --> 00:02:14,919
No.

21
00:02:16,520 --> 00:02:17,360
Mrs. Lu.

22
00:02:40,599 --> 00:02:42,919
Mu Lan, we should go.

23
00:02:43,479 --> 00:02:44,439
The guests are waiting.

24
00:02:48,479 --> 00:02:49,039
Dong Lin.

25
00:02:49,719 --> 00:02:50,879
I will do as you wish.

26
00:02:51,840 --> 00:02:53,840
But if I still can't see Liang Xiao,

27
00:02:54,520 --> 00:02:56,280
I will use the cruelest way

28
00:02:56,879 --> 00:02:58,199
to send you to hell.

29
00:03:05,919 --> 00:03:07,520
(Ladies and gentlemen,)

30
00:03:07,800 --> 00:03:09,120
(the hour's struck.)

31
00:03:09,400 --> 00:03:10,919
(Let us welcome the bride and groom!)

32
00:03:11,560 --> 00:03:13,560
(First bow to Heaven and Earth.)

33
00:03:13,680 --> 00:03:15,759
(Bravo! Bravo!)

34
