38
00:03:43,800 --> 00:03:45,120
Lu Yan, it is dangerous here.

39
00:03:45,319 --> 00:03:45,800
Go!

40
00:03:49,377 --> 00:03:52,116
♪It was me♪

41
00:03:52,276 --> 00:03:56,280
♪Fired the shot for love recklessly♪

42
00:03:56,280 --> 00:03:57,000
Are you crazy?

43
00:03:57,199 --> 00:03:58,159
Your dad's wedding!

44
00:03:58,159 --> 00:03:59,680
I'm here to attend my dad's wedding.

45
00:03:59,680 --> 00:04:03,796
♪I won't be a bird in the storm♪

46
00:04:04,244 --> 00:04:08,980
♪Nor sleep forever where shadows lie♪

47
00:04:09,268 --> 00:04:13,408
♪I only pray, in the decade to come♪

48
00:04:13,840 --> 00:04:15,479
This is outrageous!

49
00:04:15,599 --> 00:04:17,759
What a scoundrel!

50
00:04:17,920 --> 00:04:19,040
You traitorous son!

51
00:04:19,599 --> 00:04:20,639
♪Must learn the art of a silver tongue♪

52
00:04:20,639 --> 00:04:21,319
Watch out!

53
00:04:21,812 --> 00:04:22,959
♪Must have a heart like a desert♪

54
00:04:22,959 --> 00:04:23,639
Lu Yan.

55
00:04:24,199 --> 00:04:25,319
You are too presumptuous.

56
00:04:26,120 --> 00:04:27,279
To behave so outrageously

57
00:04:27,439 --> 00:04:29,399
at my wedding.

58
00:04:29,480 --> 00:04:31,600
I can no longer tolerate you.

59
00:04:32,079 --> 00:04:32,759
Someone!

60
00:04:34,868 --> 00:04:38,804
♪Though happy endings won't come♪

61
00:04:39,252 --> 00:04:41,899
♪I'll stand with you♪

62
00:04:42,050 --> 00:04:42,560
♪Pierce through the flame of the night♪

63
00:04:42,560 --> 00:04:43,079
Don't worry.

64
00:04:44,560 --> 00:04:46,240
♪Even if the road is long and far♪

65
00:04:46,240 --> 00:04:47,439
How dare you!

66
00:04:48,959 --> 00:04:49,600
Go!

67
00:04:49,600 --> 00:04:51,727
♪When all the joys and sorrows♪

68
00:04:51,839 --> 00:04:54,438
♪When the dust settles, the music ends♪

69
00:04:54,588 --> 00:04:56,781
♪This romance of bravery♪

70
00:04:56,951 --> 00:04:59,939
♪This story isn't over♪

71
00:05:00,079 --> 00:05:01,680
Is this the place for you?

72
00:05:05,139 --> 00:05:06,176
(Lu Changhe)

73
00:05:20,399 --> 00:05:21,360
Your name is Dong Lin.

74
00:05:22,480 --> 00:05:23,720
From Langshan, Qingzhou.

75
00:05:25,120 --> 00:05:25,959
Listen up.

76
00:05:26,319 --> 00:05:28,519
You are not my father.

77
00:05:28,839 --> 00:05:31,240
You just have his face.

78
00:05:32,839 --> 00:05:34,079
(Let's go back to Langshan.)

79
00:05:34,720 --> 00:05:36,279
That godforsaken place?

80
00:05:36,680 --> 00:05:37,800
Go by yourself.

81
00:05:39,319 --> 00:05:40,120
Thank you.

82
00:05:40,920 --> 00:05:42,839
Brother, someone is handing out buns.

83
00:05:43,480 --> 00:05:44,040
Take it.

84
00:05:44,319 --> 00:05:44,800
Come on.

85
00:05:46,600 --> 00:05:47,720
The rich man there

86
00:05:47,959 --> 00:05:48,800
looks like you!

87
00:05:48,920 --> 00:05:49,399
Thank you.

88
00:05:49,480 --> 00:05:50,639
Exactly the same!

89
00:05:51,279 --> 00:05:52,480
We have the same face,

90
00:05:52,720 --> 00:05:53,720
but he lives in luxury

91
00:05:53,800 --> 00:05:54,959
and gives alms to others.

92
00:05:55,800 --> 00:05:56,759
Why?

93
00:05:59,600 --> 00:06:00,480
I have an idea.

94
00:06:00,720 --> 00:06:02,079
What idea?

95
00:06:05,279 --> 00:06:07,000
Just watch.

96
00:06:09,079 --> 00:06:09,800
(Since then,)

97
00:06:10,680 --> 00:06:12,759
(you started mimicking my dad.)

98
00:06:13,319 --> 00:06:14,120
(His walk,)

99
00:06:14,800 --> 00:06:15,720
(his speech,)

100
00:06:16,519 --> 00:06:18,360
(and even the small gestures.)

101
00:06:19,439 --> 00:06:21,839
(To prevent being found out
by those close to him,)

102
00:06:22,959 --> 00:06:25,240
(you even killed my entire family.)

103
00:06:29,639 --> 00:06:31,439
You don't deserve what my dad has.

104
00:06:32,199 --> 00:06:33,199
What did you say?

105
00:06:33,600 --> 00:06:34,319
Lu Yan.

106
00:06:34,959 --> 00:06:36,519
You lusted after your stepmother.

107
00:06:36,879 --> 00:06:38,240
That's already a grave sin.

108
00:06:38,560 --> 00:06:41,199
And now you want to kill your dad?

109
00:06:41,519 --> 00:06:42,240
Mr. Ling.

110
00:06:42,759 --> 00:06:44,399
You promised me to clean him up!

111
00:06:44,600 --> 00:06:45,319
That's right.

112
00:06:46,040 --> 00:06:48,079
I did promise Changhe to help him.

113
00:06:48,399 --> 00:06:49,600
But you are Dong Lin.

114
00:06:49,959 --> 00:06:51,519
I won't help the wicked.

115
00:06:56,680 --> 00:06:58,319
So you all colluded together!

116
00:07:02,160 --> 00:07:04,639
You even skinned my dad yourself.

117
00:07:06,339 --> 00:07:06,839
Brother.

118
00:07:12,839 --> 00:07:13,759
Ten years ago,

119
00:07:14,600 --> 00:07:15,639
you killed my parents

120
00:07:16,319 --> 00:07:17,560
here in this place.

121
00:07:18,720 --> 00:07:22,079
Today I will judge you
in the same place.

122
00:07:32,279 --> 00:07:33,160
Have you been poor?

123
00:07:35,839 --> 00:07:38,360
I have. Even my wife ran away.

124
00:07:40,120 --> 00:07:41,879
Because I'm poor, I deserve to die?

125
00:07:42,680 --> 00:07:43,839
I refuse to be disrespected.

126
00:07:44,279 --> 00:07:45,600
I don't want to be worthless!

127
00:07:58,040 --> 00:07:58,680
Brother.

128
00:08:05,800 --> 00:08:06,560
Sorry.

129
00:08:09,240 --> 00:08:09,839
Forgive me.

130
00:08:09,920 --> 00:08:10,560
Brother.

131
00:08:10,800 --> 00:08:11,480
I'm sorry.

132
00:08:11,800 --> 00:08:12,240
Brother!

133
00:08:12,319 --> 00:08:13,480
Please forgive me.

134
00:08:13,680 --> 00:08:14,120
Brother.

135
00:08:15,600 --> 00:08:16,079
Brother.

136
00:08:16,800 --> 00:08:17,319
Lu Yan.

137
00:08:18,360 --> 00:08:18,759
Brother.

138
00:08:18,839 --> 00:08:19,480
Lu Yan.

139
00:08:20,000 --> 00:08:21,720
Lu Yan, forgive me.

140
00:08:23,279 --> 00:08:23,839
Brother.

141
00:08:23,839 --> 00:08:25,560
Forgive me, Lu Yan.

142
00:08:27,560 --> 00:08:28,120
- Gao Qi.
- Brother.

143
00:08:28,240 --> 00:08:29,040
- Gao Qi!
- Brother.

144
00:08:29,199 --> 00:08:29,680
Gao Qi.

145
00:08:31,319 --> 00:08:31,839
Brother.

146
00:08:34,480 --> 00:08:35,159
Don't come over!

147
00:08:38,919 --> 00:08:39,480
Let her go.

148
00:08:39,559 --> 00:08:40,279
Don't come over!

149
00:08:43,799 --> 00:08:45,399
Stop!

150
00:08:48,080 --> 00:08:48,639
Mu Lan.

151
00:09:16,279 --> 00:09:16,720
Go!

152
00:09:29,960 --> 00:09:31,320
Liang Xiao's sent to the hospital.

153
00:09:35,159 --> 00:09:35,919
Grab a bite.

154
00:09:38,240 --> 00:09:38,960
Are you okay?

155
00:09:44,000 --> 00:09:44,679
I'm fine.

156
00:09:45,679 --> 00:09:46,279
Lu Yan.

157
00:09:46,679 --> 00:09:48,360
Don't keep everything inside.

158
00:09:48,679 --> 00:09:49,600
In front of me,

159
00:09:50,080 --> 00:09:51,679
you can do or say

160
00:09:52,360 --> 00:09:53,159
whatever you want.

161
00:10:21,679 --> 00:10:22,519
Right now,

162
00:10:24,120 --> 00:10:25,200
I just want to be with you.

163
00:10:33,320 --> 00:10:34,159
In these ten years,

164
00:10:35,360 --> 00:10:37,559
I've been living in Dong Lin's shadow.

165
00:10:39,000 --> 00:10:40,480
Until I met you again,

166
00:10:41,600 --> 00:10:42,519
I didn't realize

167
00:10:43,200 --> 00:10:45,320
you suffered just like I did.

168
00:10:45,919 --> 00:10:46,919
Ten years ago,

169
00:10:48,399 --> 00:10:50,240
we both lost the people
who mattered most.

170
00:10:52,399 --> 00:10:54,080
Now, I don't want to lose you.

171
00:10:56,240 --> 00:10:56,919
So

172
00:10:59,799 --> 00:11:00,879
I can't let you go.

173
00:11:11,360 --> 00:11:12,360
I'm here for you.

174
00:11:20,200 --> 00:11:21,240
For the past ten years,

175
00:11:22,639 --> 00:11:23,679
I thought

176
00:11:24,039 --> 00:11:26,039
the only thing left in my life

177
00:11:27,159 --> 00:11:28,080
was revenge.

178
00:11:29,360 --> 00:11:29,879
But now...

179
00:11:32,240 --> 00:11:34,879
It seems like my future

180
00:11:35,360 --> 00:11:36,759
can still hold other expectations.

181
00:11:38,100 --> 00:11:39,600
♪The night in my glass is falling low♪

182
00:11:39,600 --> 00:11:40,320
Lu Yan.

183
00:11:42,080 --> 00:11:42,840
Thank you.

184
